HEADWORD: Photographometer
<hw>Pho*tog"ra*phom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Photograph</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>An instrument for determining the sensibility
